text:
Of course, I'm in great shape.
I intend to keep this state until the final day.

From the moment I wake up until I go to sleep,
I can train without any worries...

Hehe,
there's nothing more wonderful than this!

And to make sure I don't waste
a single second of this opportunity...
I've set more alarms than usual in the morning.

Wow, that's fantastic!
I'm expecting even better performance than usual.
Yes, please look forward to it!
